{"id": 1775461131824, "text": "Once upon a time, in the heart of a mist-covered forest, a **Laum\u0117** sat by a silver stream, weaving the threads of human destiny. Her hair was as long as the river, and her eyes sparkled like damp stones in the moonlight.\n\nOne evening, she heard a soft cry echoing from a nearby cottage. Curious, she drifted through the keyhole and found a wooden cradle. Inside lay a **baby**, its tiny hands reaching for the stars. The Laum\u0117 felt a strange warmth she had never known. She didn't want to steal the child; instead, she wanted to gift it the wonders of the earth.\n\nShe whispered a song into the child\u2019s ear, a melody of blooming clover and hidden treasures. With a gentle touch, she left a **golden belt** tucked into the blankets\u2014a charm to ensure the child would always find the way home through any storm.\n\nAs the morning sun began to rise, the Laum\u0117 dissolved into the morning dew, leaving behind only the scent of fresh rain and a life forever touched by the **magic of the woods**.", "voice": "am_michael", "duration": 74.26133333333334, "filename": "audio_1775461131824.wav", "word_timings": [{"word": " Once", "start": 0.0, "end": 0.38}, {"word": " upon", "start": 0.38, "end": 0.7}, {"word": " a", "start": 0.7, "end": 0.84}, {"word": " time,", "start": 0.84, "end": 1.24}, {"word": " in", "start": 1.3, "end": 1.44}, {"word": " the", "start": 1.44, "end": 1.56}, {"word": " heart", "start": 1.56, "end": 1.84}, {"word": " of", "start": 1.84, "end": 2.02}, {"word": " a", "start": 2.02, "end": 2.14}, {"word": " miscovered", "start": 2.14, "end": 2.92}, {"word": " forest,", "start": 2.92, "end": 3.2}, {"word": " a", "start": 3.76, "end": 3.86}, {"word": " asterisk", "start": 3.86, "end": 4.48}, {"word": "-asterisk", "start": 4.48, "end": 4.9}, {"word": "-lawn", "start": 4.9, "end": 5.36}, {"word": " asterisk", "start": 5.36, "end": 6.02}, {"word": "-asterisk", "start": 6.02, "end": 6.44}, {"word": " sat", "start": 6.44, 